{"tid":2237233,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"彭博 : 川普勝選的機會正在消失 而且幾乎沒有時間讓他扭轉局勢","createTime":"2020-10-10T05:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T06:18:36.000Z","uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ed15cdc6fd2d8c28dd25c9a790781324109bd571","tid":2237233,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:49:01.000Z","msg":"【彭博】-- 雖然2016年大選的教訓決定了絕不能排除唐納德&middot;川普的機會，但他的連任之路正在急劇收窄，因喬&middot;拜登領先勢頭持續擴大，而選民對總統新冠疫情的處理感到不滿。<br />\n<br />\nRealClearPolitics的統計顯示，川普現在全美範圍內平均落後於拜登9.7個百分點，在關鍵戰場州落後5至7個百分點。離投票日還剩25天，尚不清楚川普如何去收復失地。<br />\n<br />\n周四川普拒絕與拜登進行遠程辯論，令他喪失了改變戰局走勢所剩無幾的一個機會。<br />\n<br />\n「不來兩次辯論我不知道唐納德&middot;川普如何追趕喬&middot;拜登，」 共和黨民調員Frank Luntz周四對彭博電視說，「沒有那場辯論，我無法計算出他想要贏得大選就應該所處的位置。」<br />\n<br />\n仍對川普2016年戰勝希拉蕊&middot;柯林頓心有余悸的民主黨人還沒有慶祝。四年前離大選相同的時間，希拉蕊平均領先川普5.3個百分點。但這次情況大不一樣，拜登獲得的支持率遠高於希拉蕊當年，而且他在川普2016年拿下的多個州也有競爭力，這也可能會降低總統連任的機會。<br />\n<br />\n原文標題Trump&rsquo;s Chance to Win is Fading With Little Time Left to Recover<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%8B%9D%E9%81%B8%E7%9A%84%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1-%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%94%E5%B9%BE%E4%B9%8E%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E8%AE%93%E4%BB%96%E6%89%AD%E8%BD%89%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2-155858903.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25B7%259D%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%258B%259D%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A4%25B1-%25E8%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%2594%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E4%25B9%258E%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25AE%2593%25E4%25BB%2596%25E6%2589%25AD%25E8%25BD%2589%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%258B%25A2-155858903.html&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=afb7850b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%8B%9D%E9%81%B8%E7%9A%84%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1-%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%94%E5%B9%BE%E4%B9%8E%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E8%AE%93%E4%BB%96%E6%89%AD%E8%BD%89%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2-155858903.html</a>"},{"pid":"c3e3d927755811d46bb8947598f4e8c635a482c7","tid":2237233,"uid":46587,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://realclimatescience.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Screen-Shot-2017-04-01-at-9.02.52-AM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frealclimatescience.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2FScreen-Shot-2017-04-01-at-9.02.52-AM.gif&h=f223e231&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe563c18aaecae52544de76a0ae2fcf9a60dac9","tid":2237233,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:51:27.000Z","msg":"拜登幾時先宣布籌組內閣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11572a2e92dd7d10452f46cca2142a42f25ccc6a","tid":2237233,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:54:59.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎差啲整死侵侵，不過佢到而家都冇親口怪責老友，真係友情可貴，雖然人地唔當你係朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/171492/57bb6018-47a3-4363-8131-234c066fee6d@1200x1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F171492%2F57bb6018-47a3-4363-8131-234c066fee6d%401200x1200.jpg&h=7223f279&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0bef2056f5cebff9b40ab5c46714df59eb067e2","tid":2237233,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:55:17.000Z","msg":"Bloomberg 啲大選新聞biased到根本係propaganda"},{"pid":"2205f316aa5fa7f585c5bce0068536192771f5c1","tid":2237233,"uid":127575,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:56:00.000Z","msg":"Bloomberg = CNN<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33b06e05cfedd42c2bf695a6f14a5dd84e93f